/sf-bay-area-aging-demographics/","title":"This is the real doom loop. It will change everything about life in the Bay Area","abstract":"For years we’ve heard of the potential doom loop in San Francisco. But another threat has been building across the Bay Area in relative silence.","plainTextAbstract":"For years we’ve heard of the potential doom loop in San Francisco. But another threat has been building across the Bay Area in relative silence.","excerpt":"For years we’ve heard of the potential doom loop in San Francisco. But another threat has been building across the Bay Area in relative silence.","eyebrow":{"linkText":"Graying Bay","url":""},"badge":null,"displayedDate":"2025-07-14 11:00:00","authorName":"Dan Kopf","authors":[{"id":1466,"name":"Dan Kopf","title":"Senior Editor, Data and Research","url":"/author/dan-kopf/","credit":"Staff Writer","image":{"id":20731362,"url":null,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":2318,"height":2467,"guid":"photo_20731362","dirPath":"01/17/05/27/20731362/5","alt":"photo Dan Kopf from link titled \"This is the real doom loop. It will change everything about life in the Bay Area\"","title":"Dan Kopf"}},{"id":987,"name":"Roland Li","title":"Business Reporter","url":"/author/roland-li/","credit":"Staff Writer","image":{"id":18462162,"url":null,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":2048,"height":1365,"guid":"photo_18462162","dirPath":"01/06/33/27/18462162/5","alt":"San Francisco Chronicle Business reporter Roland Li is seen on Thursday, Aug. 29, 2019 in San Francisco, Calif.","title":"staff_li"}}],"bylineObjects":[{"id":1466,"name":"Dan Kopf","title":"Senior Editor, Data and Research","url":"/author/dan-kopf/","credit":"Staff Writer","image":{"id":20731362,"url":null,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":2318,"height":2467,"guid":"photo_20731362","dirPath":"01/17/05/27/20731362/5","alt":"photo Dan Kopf from link titled \"This is the real doom loop. It will change everything about life in the Bay Area\"","title":"Dan K