12377/6/rawImage.jpg","b64":null,"width":2048,"height":1478,"caption":{"plain":"Farm labor leader Cesar Chavez pickets outside the San Diego-area headquarters of Safeway markets in 1973, in protest over the arrest of 29 people at a Delano, Calif. Safeway. A New York Times investigation published Wednesday includes accusations from two women who said Chavez sexually abused them as children in the 1970s.","html1":null,"serializedReact":null},"loading":"lazy","external":null,"alt":"Farm labor leader Cesar Chavez pickets outside the San Diego-area headquarters of Safeway markets in 1973, protesting the arrest of 29 people at a Delano (Kern County) Safeway. A New York Times investigation published Wednesday includes accusations from two women who said Chavez sexually abused them as children in the 1970s.","title":"GettyImages-515109272"},"collectionConfig":{"showLabels":false,"persistentTimestamp":false,"showEyebrows":true,"showPhoto":null,"showByline":false,"showTimestamp":false,"useImg":false,"blurb":null,"useBlurb":false,"hideBlurbOnMobile":false,"forceHideEyebrows":false},"displayedDateFormat":"h:mm aaa","sponsored":null,"videoloop":null,"slideshowImages":null,"bizRelItem":null},{"__typename":"ArticleStub","type":"article","url":"/bayarea/article/dolores-huerta-chavez-abuse-22083626.php","title":"Dolores Huerta breaks decades of silence on Cesar Chavez abuse allegations","excerpt":"Dolores Huerta says she kept sexual abuse by Cesar Chavez secret for decades to protect the farmworker movement, breaking her silence after new reporting surfaced.","abstract":"\u003cp\u003eDolores Huerta says she kept sexual abuse by Cesar Chavez secret for decades to protect the farmworker movement, breaking her silence after new reporting surfaced.\u003c/p\u003e","plainTextAbstract":"Dolores Huerta says she kept sexual abuse by Cesar Chavez secret for decades to protect the farmworker movement, breaking her silence after new reporting surfaced.","displayedDate":"2026-03-18 09:30:25","la